summary:
Abbott: Strange as it may seem, they give ball players nowadays very peculiar names.
Costello: Funny names?
Abbott: Nicknames, nicknames. Now, on the St. Louis team we have Who&rsquo;s on first, What&rsquo;s on second, I Don&rsquo;t Know is on third&ndash;
Costello: That&rsquo;s what I want to find out. I want you to tell me the names of the fellows on the St. Louis team.
Abbott: I&rsquo;m telling you. Who&rsquo;s on first, What&rsquo;s on second, I Don&rsquo;t Know is on third&ndash;

content:
A notice displays information that explains nearby content. Often used to call attention to a particular detail.
When using Kramdown {: .notice} can be added after a sentence to assign the .notice to the &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; element.
Changes in Service: We just updated our privacy policy here to better service our customers. We recommend reviewing the changes. {: .notice}
Primary Notice: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. {: .notice&ndash;primary}
